title: Clinton touts State Department record to turn tables on GOP critics ahead of high-stakes hearing
text: Ahead of high-stakes testimony this week before the Republican-led House committee investigating the Benghazi attacks, former secretary of state Hillary Rodham Clinton is trying to turn the tables by highlighting the rest of her well-regarded tenure as chief U.S. diplomat.
